        <abstract>
            <p>Hooker would be very glad to see the mountain plants Fd’AF has collected.</p>
            <p>Hooker says huge cypress trunks have been found buried in the ground [in the Azores]; the site needs to be described and investigated. CD suggests collecting earth from same bed to see whether any seeds have remained viable.</p>
        </abstract>
